Package bt.module

Annotation Type ExtendedMessageHandlers


  • @Target({PARAMETER,FIELD,METHOD})
@Retention(RUNTIME)
public @interface ExtendedMessageHandlers
    Annotates individual message handlers, that work with extended protocol message types.

    Each message type is assigned a unique name, thus annotated value should be a Map<String, MessageHandler<? extends ExtendedMessage>>.

    Since:
    1.0
